Sn, and Te Isotopes at Near Threshold Energies.
Metallic samples with natural isotopic composition in
ring form. Cd - 564 g, Sn - 641 g, Te - 447 g.
and stand in COMMON section.Standard cross.section
was averaged on energy range +-10.keV near EN-NRM
